{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"4519928040","title":"攻击党委的言论","origin":"北京地质勘探学院党委会宣传部编《社会主义教育参考资料第二编：右派言论汇编》，1957年10月5日。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"c75834287b","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"4519928040"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"17d60aee8d","name":"秦培元"},{"id":"462e3992c8","name":"陈华园"},{"id":"566e9c9f66","name":"李亚玲"},{"id":"82cc012e26","name":"北京地质勘探学院"},{"id":"a81160210d","name":"陆伟文"},{"id":"be5c925d21","name":"林墨荫"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"69ea82925d","type":"title","text":"攻击党委的言论","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4519928040"},{"id":"2baac8d143","type":"authors","text":"北京地质勘探学院陆伟文陈华园秦培元李亚玲林墨荫","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4519928040"},{"id":"eae6766c91","type":"paragraph","text":"陆伟文说：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4519928040"},{"id":"7bb370f6a8","type":"paragraph","text":"“一般党员水平低一些是可以，而党委的一些人比群众高明不了多少，思想是这样，讲话也是这样，什么‘文件擦亮了眼睛’、‘总路线是灯塔’，现在又是‘鸣’‘放’，都是跟着上级讲，没有自己的语言。”","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4519928040"},{"id":"c4a86c73de","type":"paragraph","text":"“中国共产党有办法，拿出12．5亿买人心（指一九五六年的工资改革）不然就会出匈牙利事件，这是吸取波匈教训。”","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4519928040"},{"id":"3b00a085c4","type":"paragraph","text":"秦培元说：","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4519928040"},{"id":"3fd1a7684c","type":"paragraph","text":"“党委表现非常不愿领导似的，党委应深入看大字报内容，我就没有见到党委来看过，不知他们在干些什么？党委要辛苦点，休息时就不要回家和老婆女儿在一起，要下来和职工同学一起吃饭睡觉，深入了解情况，到生动的场合受教育。”","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4519928040"},{"id":"9bd3312d6b","type":"paragraph","text":"“刘颕、王庆华革命就是为了自己的享受。”","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4519928040"},{"id":"455bd6baa8","type":"paragraph","text":"陈华园说：","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4519928040"},{"id":"3c303611e7","type":"paragraph","text":"“党委在会上干一套在会下又干一套，以后谁也不相信他们（指党委）了，报告我也不鼓掌。”","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4519928040"},{"id":"1bd221a819","type":"paragraph","text":"李亚玲说：","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4519928040"},{"id":"5effc0d4d2","type":"appellation","text":"“陈子谷简直成了土皇帝。”","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4519928040"},{"id":"86edb67841","type":"paragraph","text":"“党员谈一套理论是说教，问题不在说多少，而是作多少，党员只会说，不会作。”","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4519928040"},{"id":"6e82914b3a","type":"paragraph","text":"林墨荫说：","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4519928040"},{"id":"f4f5b29625","type":"paragraph","text":"“学校领导同志来院作的第一次报告是好的，以后的脏衣服就出来了，如刘型、刘普伦。”","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4519928040"},{"id":"d21e2b2d88","type":"paragraph","text":"“韩代望是又狼心又愚蠢。”","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4519928040"},{"id":"db286a521b","type":"paragraph","text":"“王哲民是共产主义的败类”","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4519928040"},{"id":"3a13a99e5f","type":"paragraph","text":"党员和积极分子象粪蛆一样，忙忙碌碌，挤来挤去慢慢往往上爬，在中间就跌下来了，以后又挤来挤去，慢慢往上爬，在中间又跌下来了，“最后往上爬，爬到边缘就变成了一个苍蝇飞起了。”","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4519928040"},{"id":"dbea039734","type":"paragraph","text":"“池际尚先生就是往上爬，你真和国民党一样”。","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4519928040"},{"id":"418049e08d","type":"paragraph","text":"林墨荫在中条山遇见一位党员工农干部，说林是官僚主义。林回校后说“我恨不得把他的头打烂”。","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4519928040"}],"page":{"id":"fda35ae08a","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4519928040","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}